caption.text:
سخت تمرین می‌کنی، تغذیه‌تو رعایت می‌کنی، به برنامه‌ت پایبندی…
ولی هنوز اون نتیجه‌ای که می‌خوای رو نمی‌بینی؟

🔍 شاید مشکل از تمرینت نیست — از خوابه!

خواب روی ریکاوری، چربی‌سوزی، رشد عضله و حتی هورمون‌ها تأثیر مستقیم داره.
بدون خواب باکیفیت، بدن نمی‌تونه درست عمل کنه؛ حتی اگه سخت‌ترین تمرین‌ها رو انجام بدی.

💬 حالا نوبت توئه:
شما شبی چند ساعت می‌خوابی؟ حس می‌کنی کافیه؟

کامنت بذار 👇 ببینیم بقیه تو چه وضعی‌ان!

——————
Film by @amirblackbox 
——————
You train hard, eat clean, stay disciplined…
But still not seeing the results you’re aiming for?

🔍 Maybe the issue isn’t your workout — it’s your sleep.

Sleep impacts recovery, fat loss, muscle growth, and hormones.
Without enough quality rest, your body can’t perform — no matter how hard you train.

💬 Now your turn:
How many hours do you sleep at night? Do you think it’s enough?

Drop your answer below 👇 Let’s see what the rest of us are dealing with too!

#SleepBetter #RecoveryMatters #SmartTraining #SleepForGains #ZMA #Melatonin #GABA

caption.text:
Relax Your Neck & Shoulders Before Bed — With Just a Pillow
End your day with these gentle stretches to:
✅ Release neck and shoulder tension
✅ Improve posture after long hours sitting
✅ Promote deep relaxation for better sleep

All you need is a soft pillow and 5 quiet minutes.

Save this simple routine & sleep better tonight!

#NeckRelief #ShoulderStretch #BetterPosture #EveningRoutine #SleepBetter #GentleExercise #RelaxAndUnwind #healthyaging

caption.text:
💥Tired, wired, moody… and your jeans feel tighter overnight? You’re not broken—your body’s just asking for help.

If you’re 40+ and feeling flat, puffy, snappy, and like sleep just isn’t working anymore… it’s time.

My 30-Day RESET isn’t a diet. It’s a science-backed, realistic program to help:
⚡ Rebuild real energy
😴 Sleep deeper and wake fresher
💃 Balance moods
⚖️ Release stubborn weight that’s hanging around your belly

We’re not doing restriction—we’re doing nourishment, balance, and results that last. Even if you stick to it 80% you will still get great results.  Yes I know that you are already busy and I am a realistic naturopath. 

Comment “RESET” 👇👇👇 to find out if this is for you. It’s time to feel like you again and not just keep wondering "Is this as good as it gets?".

#thepresentdaywisewoman #bamreset #over40health #hormonebalance  #energyreset #sleepbetter #moodboost #naturalweightloss #perimenopausehealth #womensupportingwomen #menopause #thepresentdaywisewoman #jenthenaturopath #energy #sleep

☀️ Morning Sunlight: A Free Brain Tonic

Catching morning sunlight isn’t just about vitamin D—it’s one of the most powerful natural therapies for your brain.

🧠 How It Helps Brain Health:
✅ Regulates Circadian Rhythm Morning light hits your retina and resets your biological clock. This boosts alertness during the day and improves deep sleep at night—vital for memory and cognition.

✅ Boosts Serotonin Early sunlight stimulates serotonin release—a neurotransmitter that stabilizes mood, promotes calm, and keeps depression at bay.
 
✅ Enhances Dopamine Activity Light exposure helps regulate dopamine, improving focus, motivation, and even motor function. Especially useful in patients at risk for Parkinson’s.

✅ Improves Vitamin D Production Low vitamin D is linked to brain fog, depression, and even dementia. Just 15–20 minutes of morning sun helps keep levels optimal.
 
✅ Reduces Risk of Neurodegeneration Better sleep, better mood, and better hormones all translate to long-term brain protection.

⏰ Best time? Between 6:30 am and 8:30 am, for about 15–30 minutes. No sunscreen. Let the light hit your eyes (not direct staring—just ambient light exposure).

💡 Bottom line: Skip the scroll. Step outside. Your brain will thank you later.

caption.text:
¿El descanso es la clave para la productividad?
Te compartimos una herramienta sencilla que alinea tus prioridades diarias con tus horas de sueño para que rindas al máximo, basada en lo que aprendimos en la entrevista con el @dr.eduardestivill
Descárgala GRATIS al suscribirte a la newsletter semanal (enlace en bio) y encuentra la entrevista completa en nuestro canal de YouTube: Morir de Éxito.

caption.text:
تا حالا کسی بهت گفته چغندر می‌تونه خواب، انرژی، تمرکز و حتی پوستتو بهتر کنه؟
منم نمی‌دونستم…
تا وقتی یکی از دوستام که هیچ‌وقت قرص و مکمل نمی‌خوره، این تجربه عجیبش رو باهام به اشتراک گذاشت.
فقط با خوردن چغندر طبیعی. نه پودر، نه دارو، فقط یه خوراکی ساده که همیشه جلو چشمم بود.

نتیجه‌شو توی پست توضیح دادم — ورق بزن ببین چی شد.

این پست مخصوص توئه اگه:
✔️ زود خسته می‌شی
✔️ خواب آرومی نداری
✔️ حس می‌کنی انرژیت ته کشیده
✔️ دنبال یه راه طبیعی، ساده و واقعی می‌گردی

اگه برات جالب بود، پست رو ذخیره کن، بفرست واسه یکی که بهش نیاز داره
و اگه از این تجربه‌ها خوشت میاد، پیجم رو فالو کن—هنوز کلی چیز نگفته دارم برات!

⸻

Ever heard that beets can improve your sleep, energy, focus, and even your skin?
I hadn’t either—
until a friend of mine (who literally never takes pills or supplements) shared her story with me.
No powders, no meds—just real, natural beetroot.
And the way it helped her body? Honestly, amazing.

Swipe through to read what changed for her.

This post is for you if:
✔️ You feel drained or sluggish
✔️ Your sleep is off
✔️ Your focus and mood are low
✔️ You want a natural, realistic way to feel better

Save this post, share it with someone who needs it,
and if you like real, simple wellness tips—hit that follow. I’ve got more stories coming.

caption.text:
Here is a simple technique to teach 
tongue suction ⤵️ 

Before I get into it, you will want to SAVE this post for later & FOLLOW so you don’t miss out on more tips like this 😀

Here it is ⤵️

1. Start with tongue clicks. You want to make sure that the clicks are done without any compensations. No jaw shifting or jaw protrusion.

2.  If a child can’t click- place a small candy on the middle of the tongue. (I said if a child can’t do it. But I also use it with adults that can’t click).

Instruct the patient to suck real hard on the candy without using the lips so the tongue suctions when sucking hard.

3. Once the patient is able to click. Ask them to hold the tongue up for longer and not click the tongue right away, holding the suction longer and longer each session. Goal is to hold the suction for 1-2 minutes.

Can you suction your tongue ❓
.
.
.
.
.
.

سخت تمرین می‌کنی، تغذیه‌تو رعایت می‌کنی، به برنامه‌ت پایبندی…
ولی هنوز اون نتیجه‌ای که می‌خوای رو نمی‌بینی؟

🔍 شاید مشکل از تمرینت نیست — از خوابه!

خواب روی ریکاوری، چربی‌سوزی، رشد عضله و حتی هورمون‌ها تأثیر مستقیم داره.
بدون خواب باکیفیت، بدن نمی‌تونه درست عمل کنه؛ حتی اگه سخت‌ترین تمرین‌ها رو انجام بدی.

💬 حالا نوبت توئه:
شما شبی چند ساعت می‌خوابی؟ حس می‌کنی کافیه؟

کامنت بذار 👇 ببینیم بقیه تو چه وضعی‌ان!

But still not seeing the results you’re aiming for?

🔍 Maybe the issue isn’t your workout — it’s your sleep.

product.name: Red Light Therapy Panel Pro - Small
product.description:
Introducing the Pro Red Light Therapy Panel Small, on a Stand

Applications 💥

	* Relieve pain and discomfort for enhanced mobility.
	* Promote skin rejuvenation and a more youthful appearance.
	* Boost overall vitality and well-being.
	* Target specific wellness goals with precision.
	* Enjoy the benefits of light therapy in a compact design.

Specifications

	*  Irradiance: 216mw/cm2 @ 2 inches
	*  Wavelength: 660&850nm, or 5 wavelength (630, 660, 810, 830, 850nm)
	*  LEDs and lasers: 60pcs 3W
	*  Size: 29 x 21 x 6.5 cm
	*  Warranty: 3 year

Key Features 🌟

Multispectrum Advantage: Benefit from the therapeutic potential of wavelengths ranging from 660nm to 850nm, ideal for a range of applications.

Compact and Portable: Designed to fit seamlessly into your lifestyle, with its size making it easy to use and transport.

caption.text:
This is my most asked question...

"When should you take magnesium? It depends on the type and your goal"

🧠 Magnesium Glycinate
– Calms the nervous system
– Helps with anxiety, sleep, and stress
– Take at night 🌙

⚡ Magnesium Malate
– Boosts energy + supports muscles
– Great for fatigue, pain, and performance
– Take in the morning ☀️

💩 Magnesium Citrate
– Supports digestion + relieves constipation
– May cause loose stools
– Take in the morning or as needed 💧

🧬 Magnesium Threonate
– Crosses the blood-brain barrier
– Supports focus, memory, and cognition
– Take in the morning ☀️

🦴 Magnesium Oxide
– Least absorbable but often used for constipation
– Not ideal for daily use
– Use short-term only 🚫

Your body reacts differently to each form—so timing does matter.

Save this as your magnesium cheat sheet & drop a comment if you're still unsure which one’s right for you 

#magnesiumbenefits #sleepbetter #energyboost #supplements #healthtips

Comment ‘HORMONE’ to learn more about naturally balancing your hormones using food, herbs, and lifestyle medicine.

caption.text:
Real recovery doesn’t exi—

Wait, actually it does.

Meet the formula your nervous system has been dreaming of. 💤

Formulated with Ashwagandha, L-Theanine, NAC, Crocetin and Magnesium, Sleep Better targets the root causes of poor sleep: cortisol dysregulation, nervous system overstimulation, and impaired melatonin cycles. This isn’t just about falling asleep—it is about unlocking the cellular repair processes that only happen when you actually rest.

#sleepbetter #newsupplement #new #ashwagandha #rest #sleep #nac #longevityresearch #recovery #fyp

This smartwatch has completely transformed my routine! Here’s why I’m loving it: 💡⌚️✨ 

💖 Health Monitoring: Tracks my heart rate and blood oxygen 24/7, plus gives a detailed sleep analysis. It’s like having a health coach on my wrist! 🩺💤

📞 Stay Connected: With its built-in speaker and Bluetooth, I can make/answer calls, play music, and get notifications from all my socials like Instagram, WhatsApp, and more—directly from my wrist. Vibrations ensure I never miss a thing! 📱🎶

🏃‍♀️ Sports Pro: 112 sports modes (yes, 112!) for activities like running, cycling, basketball, and more. Tracks steps, heart rate, calories, and distance perfectly. And it’s waterproof (IP68), so it’s my companion rain or shine! 🏋️‍♂️🚴‍♀️💦

⏰ Your Daily Assistant: Loaded with useful features like an alarm clock, stopwatch, weather updates, camera control, music control, and even a phone finder—it’s my ultimate productivity partner. 💼

📸 Style & Display: The 1.85-inch HD color screen is stunning, and with 200+ dials to choose from, I can switch up my look daily. I even added a personal photo for a unique touch! 🌟🖼️

🔋 Battery Life: Lasts 7–15 days on one charge, which is amazing for a feature-packed smartwatch like this. 🚀

Highly recommend this for anyone looking for an all-in-one fitness and lifestyle companion!”

Link: https://www.amazon.de/-/en/Smartwatch-Womens-Fitness-Watch-Function/dp/B0DB1436K8/

caption.text:
Tired but finding it hard to sleep? Day 23 of our winter wellbeing advent calendar and it’s all about sleeeeeeep. Did you know that we need more sleep in winter? But this time of year is so full of stimulation and excitement that sleep might feel hard to come by right now. I hope these mantras will give you something calming to anchor on. While you’re here let me share with you my top tip for promoting better sleep. Your ability to sleep is a function of your ability to relax so the more you build your “relaxation muscles” during the day, the easier it’ll be to relax and fall asleep at night. So scroll back through my feed and try the plethora of calming practices and repeat them regularly through your day - the chicken wing shoulder rolls, the face hug, the hand on heart while you drink, the candle breath… make space for these and notice how it’s easier to switch off when your head hits the pillow. Try them and let me know how you go.
Last day tomorrow! Drop me a ♥️ if you’ve enjoyed this series.
All the love,
Suz x

caption.text:
Yes, clearing off your nightstand might actually help you sleep better tonight.

Clutter isn’t just a visual thing. It affects how our brains process information, how easily we get distracted, and even how well we can relax.

And when your space is constantly reminding you of what needs to be done… your brain stays in “go” mode, even when your body is ready to crash.

Start small:

▶️ Clear your bedroom floor
▶️ Put away the laundry pile
▶️ Toss or rehome anything on your nightstand that doesn’t belong

Think of it like clearing your mental inbox. You deserve to rest in a space that feels calm, not chaotic.

Want more no-stress tips like this? Hit follow and share this with a friend who’s been feeling stuck in the clutter loop.
